welcome_message_body: "Welcome to Sumner, the charming city known for its beautiful historic downtown and friendly community. We hope you have a wonderful time exploring all that Sumner has to offer!"

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at McChord AFB Airport serves both commercial and military flights.

terminals.name: Military Terminal
terminals.description: The military terminal at McChord AFB Airport is used exclusively for military flights.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Seattle-Tacoma International Airport houses the majority of the airport's facilities, including check-in counters, baggage claim, and a variety of dining and shopping options.

terminals.name: North Satellite Terminal
terminals.description: The North Satellite Terminal at Seattle-Tacoma International Airport primarily serves Alaska Airlines and its regional partners, with a variety of gates and amenities for passengers.

terminals.name: South Satellite Terminal
terminals.description: The South Satellite Terminal at Seattle-Tacoma International Airport is primarily used for international flights, with a variety of gates and facilities for travelers.

wifi.note: Passengers can connect to the airport's free WiFi network after watching a short advertisement.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Renton Airport serves all commercial and private flights.

terminals.name: Private Terminal
terminals.description: The private terminal at Renton Airport is reserved for private and charter flights.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Boeing Field/King County International Airport is a modern and efficient facility, serving both commercial and general aviation flights.

terminals.name: North Terminal
terminals.description: The North Terminal at Boeing Field/King County International Airport is primarily used for general aviation and private flights, with a separate entrance and parking area.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport, with no time limit.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Kenmore Air Harbor SPB Airport serves as the primary hub for all incoming and outgoing flights.

terminals.name: Seaplane Terminal
terminals.description: The seaplane terminal at Kenmore Air Harbor SPB Airport is where all seaplane flights depart and arrive.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Bremerton Airport serves all commercial and private flights.

terminals.name: Private Terminal
terminals.description: The private terminal at Bremerton Airport caters to private and charter flights.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.
